        <h2>The rule-breaking Sisters Grimke</h2> 
        <h3>How 19th-century women got political</h3> 
        <div class="meta">
          February 26, 2015 | 
         <span class="label editorpick">Editor's Pick</span> 
         <span class="label popular">Popular</span> 
        </div>
        <!--/.meta--> 
       </div>
